%20across%2090%20countries.%3Cp%3EOmar%20Vega%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilding-pickleball-courts-luxury-real-estate-development-amenity-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epickleball%20tore%20through%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20crazed%20developers%20and%20homeowners%20building%20new%20and%20converting%20old%20courts%20left%20and%20right%20to%20cater%20to%20its%204.8%20million%20US%20players%2C%20padel%20has%20had%20a%20less%20accelerated%20rise%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20estimated%20that%2C%20as%20of%20May%2C%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F05%2F11%2Fsports%2Ftennis%2Fpickleball-platform-tennis-padel.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20200%20courts%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Globally%2C%20at%20least%2C%20the%20sport%20is%20more%20well-known.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarko%20Gojanovic%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20with%20One%20Sotheby's%20International%20Realty%20in%20Miami%20Beach%2C%20said%20padel%20is%20becoming%20so%20big%20in%20the%20South%20Florida%20city%20because%20it's%20familiar%20to%20foreign%20homebuyers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-luxury-real-estate-condos-colombia-argentina-investment-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edriving%20sales%20at%20pricey%20condo%20towers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20amenity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20that%20are%20playing%20the%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20Gojanovic%20said.%20%26quot%3BMiami's%20full%20of%20South%20Americans%20and%20Europeans%20that%20have%20been%20playing%20padel%20since%20they%20were%20young.%20So%20it's%20like%20a%20sport%20that's%20reintroduced%20to%20them.%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%20it%20became%20super%20popular.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuyers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fturnberryoneparktower.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOne%20Park%20Tower%20by%20Turnberry%20at%20SoL%C3%A9%20Mia%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20North%20Miami%20were%20clamoring%20for%20padel%2C%20according%20to%20Aly-khan%20Merali%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CFO%20of%20Turnberry%2C%20the%20developer%20behind%20the%20tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20residential%20tower%20in%20Miami.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581c760a79e5746976af590%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReserve%20Padel%20will%20have%20a%20new%20facility%20near%20the%20tower.%3Cp%3EOne%20Park%20Tower%20by%20Turnberry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2033-story%20condo%20building%2C%20where%20one-bedroom%20apartments%20start%20at%20%24800%2C000%2C%20has%20a%20range%20of%20amenities%20like%20a%20golf%20simulator%2C%20shopping%2C%20and%20a%20wellness%20center.%20Now%20Reserve%20Padel%20is%20constructing%20a%20new%20location%20just%20steps%20from%20the%20tower%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Turnberry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20demand%20for%20padel%20%E2%80%94%20we%20researched%20it%2C%20we%20saw%20how%20busy%20they%20were%20at%20their%20other%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20Merali%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20recently%20started%20playing%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Spain%20last%20summer%20and%20I%20saw%20it%20everywhere.%20As%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20I%20think%20you'll%20be%20surprised%20as%20to%20how%20quickly%20it%20grows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F111w57.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E111%20West%2057th%20Street%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20skyscraper%20off%20of%20Central%20Park%20where%20available%20condos%20range%20from%20%248.5%20million%20to%20%2454.6%20million%2C%20has%20a%20private%20padel%20court%20for%20residents.%20And%20Enclave%2C%20a%20gated%20community%20about%2035%20miles%20from%20Chicago%20in%20South%20Barrington%2C%20Illinois%2C%20will%20also%20have%20a%20communal%20padel%20court.%20A%20home%20within%20the%20high-end%20community%20is%20currently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.compass.com%2Flisting%2F14-enclave-south-barrington-il-60010%2F1344229272033216521%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eon%20the%20market%20for%20%243.5%20million%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20outdoor%20padel%20court.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658323e4cefc010bea25a512%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20private%20padel%20court%20at%203065%20East%20Lake%20Road%20in%20Skaneateles%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EMichael%20DeRosa%20%26amp%3B%20Kelli%20Ide%20%2F%20Michael%20DeRosa%20Exchange%2C%20LLC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPadel%20isn't%20just%20being%20added%20to%20condo%20developments%20and%20private%20communities.%20Some%20homeowners%20have%20glommed%20onto%20the%20trend%2C%20too.%20A%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.michaelderosapresentations.com%2F3065-e-lake-road-skaneateles-ny-13152%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E4%2C000-square-foot%20waterfront%20home%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20sprawling%20lot%20that's%20on%20the%20market%20for%20%247%20million%20in%20Skaneateles%2C%20New%20York%2C%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20private%20padel%20court.%20A%20stately%2C%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ansleyre.com%2F7311139%2F225-valley-road-nw-atlanta-georgia-30305-fmls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E13%2C000-square-foot%20house%20in%20Atlanta%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20nine%20bedrooms%2C%20on%20the%20market%20for%20%2411.5%20million%2C%20offers%20one%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGojanovic%20said%20that%20he%20knew%20of%20a%20homeowner%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20who%20was%20an%20avid%20pickleb