0version%20of%20the%20popular%20Herm%C3%A8s%20handbag.%20The%20one%2C%20which%20is%20available%2C%20lacks%20the%20diamond%20hardware%20that%20Nicole%20Pollard's%20client%20wanted%20and%20is%20a%20slightly%20different%20model%20than%20the%20requested%20Birkin.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nicolle%20Pollard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWinston%20Chesterfield%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Barton%2C%20a%20London%20consulting%20firm%20focused%20on%20the%20wealthy%2C%20knows%20one%20Herm%C3%A8s%20collector%20whose%20husband%20gets%20her%20a%20new%20color%20handbag%20from%20the%20French%20house%20every%20year%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20a%20selection%20of%20luxury%20goods%20and%20tchotchkes%20in%20the%20same%20hue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20hits%2C%20Lalaluxe's%20Pollard%20said%2C%20are%20things%20that%20can%20be%20personalized%2C%20whether%20that%20means%20literally%20%E2%80%94%20monogrammed%20Goyard%20luggage%20that%20costs%20over%20%2410%2C000%20or%20a%20gift%20hamper%20full%20of%20items%20with%20the%20recipient's%20zodiac%20sign%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20or%20just%20something%20tailored%20to%20someone's%20hobbies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20the%20thought%20that%20goes%20into%20a%20gift%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20size%2C%20really%20stops%20them%20in%20their%20tracks%2C%26quot%3B%20Pollard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20family%20that%20loves%20to%20hike%20may%20give%20each%20other%20the%20very%20best%20outdoor%20gear%20from%20brands%20like%20Moncler%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-luxury-explained-which-brands-will-benefit-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELoro%20Piana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chesterfield%20said.%20Foodies%20may%20gift%20balsamic%20vinegar%20flown%20in%20directly%20from%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20other%20hobby-inspired%20gifts%20are%20more%20billionaire-coded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20vineyard%20in%20Tuscany%20for%20an%20oenophile.%20Knightsbridge%20Circle%20helped%20facilitate%20the%20purchase%20of%20a%20%245%20million%20site%20as%20a%20Christmas%20gift%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20mansion%20where%20Napoleon%20once%20stayed%2C%20plus%20its%20own%20honey%20and%20olive%20oil%20production%20facilities.%20The%20pricetag%20makes%20the%20%2450%2C000%20annual%20membership%20fee%20for%20Knightsbridge%20Circle's%20services%20look%20like%20a%20bargain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHave%20a%20loved%20one%20who's%20into%20racehorses%3F%20Fly%20them%20to%20a%20top%20stable%2C%20have%20them%20meet%20with%20the%20jockeys%2C%20and%20for%20the%20party%20favor%3A%20a%20steed%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chance%20to%20meet%20and%20learn%20from%20the%20best%20of%20the%20best%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20lessons%20at%20a%20turntable%20from%20a%20celebrity%20DJ%20or%20a%20cooking%20class%20with%20a%20Michelin-starred%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20is%20another%20popular%20present%20that%20can%20run%20into%20the%20high%20six%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20cost%20an%20absolute%20bomb%2C%26quot%3B%20Barton's%20Chesterfield%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperiences%20reign%20supreme%20for%20billionaires%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20everyone%2C%20and%20of%20course%20to%20the%20uberwealthy%2C%20time%20is%20your%20most%20precious%20commodity%2C%26quot%3B%20Knightsbridge%20Circle's%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20the%20price%20of%20time%20is%20measurable.%20An%20hour%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-flying-on-private-jet-compares-to-flying-business-class-2023-3%23here-are-the-biggest-differences-ive-found-when-traveling-in-business-class-vs-on-a-private-jet-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20plane%20from%20Vistajet%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20example%2C%20starts%20at%20%2411%2C000.%20One%20of%20Chesterfield's%20contacts%2C%20who%20didn't%20want%20to%20shell%20out%20to%20buy%20a%20jet%2C%20gave%20his%20daughter%20about%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%20worth%20of%20hours%20after%20she%20got%20used%20to%20flying%20private%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20intangible%20value%20of%20time%20well-spent%20is%20what%20the%20rich%20really%20covet%2C%20with%20all%20of%20the%20experts%20that%20BI%20spoke%20with%20saying%20that%20there's%20a%20general%20move%20away%20from%20gifting%20items%20and%20toward%20gifting%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20exhausted%20with%20what%20you'd%20call%20hard%20luxury%2C%26quot%3B%20Chesterfield%20said.%20The%20pandemic%20seems%20to%20have%20exacerbated%20the%20experience%20trend%2C%20too.%20One%20wealthy%20woman%2C%20he%20said%2C%20told%20her%20husband%20she%20wants%20no%20more%20jewelry%20after%20spending%20months%20locked%20inside%20buying%20luxurious%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20family%20that%20Chesterfield%20works%20with%20rented%20a%20private%20island%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20he%20said%20yoga%20retreats%20and%20wellness%20breaks%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20trip%20to%20Rishikesh%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20yoga%2C%20to%20a%20father-son%20cycling%20excursion%20in%20Mallorca%20%E2%80%94%20are%20growing%20in%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Brown's%20clients%20hire%20private%20villas%20in%20conservancies%20in%20Africa%2C%20like%20Ol%20Jogi%20in%20Kenya%20or%20Saanane%20Island%20in%20Tanzania%2C%20which%20can%20run%20up%20to%20%2440%2C000%20a%20night.%20Still%2C%20she%20clarified%20that%20the%20stay%20(and%20the%20possibility%20of%20glimpsing%20wildlife%20from%20your%20breakfast%20table)%20is%20typically%20not%20the%20only%20gift%20they%20are%20getting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20further%20from%20home%2C%20Pollard%20has%20one%20client%20who%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-zero-gravity-space-blue-origin-womb-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraveling%20to%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20holiday%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ultimate%20flex%20for%20the%20billionaire%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rich%20are%20racing%20against%20the%20effects%20of%20global%20warming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClimate%20change%20concerns%20are%20reflected%20in%20the%20types%20of%20travel%20experience%20people%20are%20giving%2C%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Brush%20for%20clients%20to%20see%20things%20before%20they're%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20Pollard%20said.%20Instead%20of%20a%20regular%20superyacht%20in%20St.%20Barths%2C%20they're%20chartering%20an%20expedition%20superyacht%20to%20see%20the%20glaciers%20in%20Antarctica%20or%20Patagonia%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20are%20going%20to%20Australia%20to%20see%20the%20Great%20Barrier%20Reef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20also%20those%20who%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20just%20think%20it's%20all%20a%20little%20tacky%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20forgoing%20big%20gifts%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20noticed%20this%20year%20people%20just%20being%20much%20less%20acquisitive%20and%20a%20bit%20more%20restrained%2C%26quot%3B%20Chesterfield%20said.%20Christmas%20has%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20just%20too%20commercial%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20take%20a%20leaf%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-christmas-gifts-sees-candies-dresses-10000-cash-2019-12-1028780601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett's%3C%2Fa%3E%20gift%20guide.%20The%20Oracle%20of%20Omaha%20famously%20used%20to%20give%20each%20of%20his%20family%20members%20%2410%2C000%20in%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20but%20after%20he%20learned%20they%20were%20blowing%20it%2C%20switched%20it%20up%20and%20now%20gives%20stock%20to%20some%20and%20chocolate%20to%20others.%20Bill%20Gates%20suggests%20books%20to%20enjoy%20over%20the%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20family%20Chesterfield%20knows%20is%20doing%20a%20Secret%20Santa%20with%20a%20%2410%20spe