3Cp%3EInternet%20access%20is%20essential%20for%20modern%20life%2C%20Sampath%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20kid%20doesn't%20have%20connectivity%20earlier%2C%20he%20can't%20play%20video%20games%2C%20do%20homework.%20If%20there%20is%20no%20connectivity%2C%20a%20mom%20cannot%20log%20into%20a%20Zoom%20call%20from%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Sampath%20said.%20%26quot%3BConnectivity%20is%20the%20bridge%20to%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternet%20access%20is%20so%20important%20that%20people%20are%20unwilling%20to%20settle%20for%20bad%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Good%20enough'%20is%20really%20not%20good%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCustomers%20want%20the%20best%20and%20they're%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20little%20more%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20took%20on%20his%20new%20role%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESampath%20worked%20at%20Verizon%20stores%20and%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20overseas%20call%20centers.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20as%20good%20of%20a%20salesman%20as%20I%20thought%20I%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20been%20a%20good%20start.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Sampath's%20goals%20is%20to%20simplify.%20To%20him%2C%20that%20includes%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20workers%20%26quot%3Breduce%20cognitive%20load%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20all%20the%20information%20they%20must%20keep%20in%20their%20heads%20and%20relay%20to%20fellow%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eemployees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESampath's%202024%20goal%20is%20for%20Verizon%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20best%20AI-applied%20company%26quot%3B%20and%20use%20it%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20first%20within%20internal%20workflows%2C%20then%20for%20customer%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20very%20bold%20ambition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20first%2C%20it's%20imperative%20to%20test%20out%20AI-driven%20processes%20with%20%26quot%3Bpilots%20and%20trials.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20put%20them%20in%20production%2C%20responsibly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20the%20algo%20doing%20things%20I%20wouldn't%20do%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESampath's%20insights%20are%20part%20of%20BI's%20year-end%20leadership%20package%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024%26quot%3B%20that%20digs%20into%20vision%2C%20strategy%2C%20and%20challenges%20across%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20you%20most%20excited%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20best%20AI-applied%20company.%20I%20think%20there's%20something%20interesting%20about%20AI%3A%20Everyone%20talks%20about%20it.%20Everyone%20claims%20they%20love%20technology%2C%20but%20no%20one's%20using%20it%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gap%20between%20technology%20and%20adoption%20is%20never%20this%20big.%20Even%20previous%20technology%20jumps%20%E2%80%94%20there%20was%20always%20a%20little%20gap%20between%20the%20technology's%20greatness%20and%20adoption.%20Here%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20light%20years%20ahead%20of%20what's%20being%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20to%20adopt%20it%20at%20scale%20and%20for%20production%20%E2%80%94%20for%20our%20sales%2C%20service%20teams%2C%20and%20install%20teams%20are%20going%20to%20be%20supercritical.%20We're%20doing%20ungodly%20amounts%20of%20work%20to%20make%20that%20happen%20in%202024.%20We'd%20probably%20be%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20to%20do%20it%20at%20the%20scale%20we're%20working%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20my%20reps%20and%20call%20centers%20and%20salespeople%20to%20use%20it.%20Second%2C%20I%20want%20to%20infuse%20it%20deep%20into%20the%20product%20stack.%20I've%20got%20six%20or%20seven%20very%20clear%20use