hich%20ones%20bought%20in%2C%20and%20which%20cashed%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFirms%20tied%20to%20David%20Tepper%20and%20Philippe%20Laffont%20held%20onto%20Nvidia%2C%20while%20others%20exited%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Tesla%20ranked%20among%20the%20stock%20market's%20best%20performers%20this%20year%2C%20as%20investors%20wagered%20the%20trio%20would%20be%20big%20winners%20from%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20the%20holdings%20of%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20and%20most%20sophisticated%20investors%20by%20Markets%20Insider%20found%20that%20some%20managers%20are%20true%20believers%20in%20the%20tech%2C%20while%20others%20were%20able%20to%20use%20the%20market's%20giddiness%20to%20pull%20in%20big%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20mentioned%20either%20declined%20to%20comment%20or%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENvidia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20maker%20of%20graphics%20chips%20has%20seen%20an%20explosion%20of%20demand%20from%20companies%20building%20all%20kinds%20of%20AI%20applications%2C%20from%20self-driving%20cars%20and%20humanoid%20robots%20to%20virtual%20chatbots.%20Its%20stock%20price%20has%20surged%20by%20about%20230%25%20this%20year%2C%20lifting%20its%20market%20capitalization%20to%20around%20%241.2%20trillion%2C%20and%20making%20it%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20best%20performer%20of%202023%20by%20a%20wide%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20raft%20of%20top-flight%20investors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-ai-stock-portfolio-q2-loeb-tepper-simons-soros-tudor-2023-8%5C%22%3Epiled%20into%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year.%20They%20included%20firms%20tied%20to%20Dan%20Loeb%2C%20Jim%20Simons%2C%20Paul%20Tudor%20Jones%2C%20Stanley%20Druckenmiller%2C%20Steve%20Cohen%2C%20David%20Tepper%2C%20Jeremy%20Grantham%20and%20George%20Soros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Tepper's%20Appaloosa%20Management%20went%20from%20owning%20zero%20Nvidia%20shares%20to%20holding%20150%2C000%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%20and%20more%20than%201%20million%20shares%20worth%20over%20%24400%20million%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%20and%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20holdings%20of%20Simons'%20Renaissance%20Technologies%20went%20from%20fewer%20than%204%2C000%20shares%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%20to%201.9%20million%20three%20months%20later.%20It%20still%20owned%201.2%20million%20Nvidia%20shares%20worth%20%24526%20million%20on%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhilippe%20Laffont's%20Coatue%20Management%20counted%20the%20chipmaker%20as%20its%20biggest%20public-market%20position%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20after%20the%20firm%20increased%20its%20stake%20by%20more%20than%20a%20million%20shares%20over%20the%20preceding%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlen%20Kacher's%20Light%20Street%20had%20Nvidia%20as%20the%20biggest%20position%20in%20its%20public%20portfolio%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20after%20first%20investing%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202022.%20The%20stake%20has%20driven%20the%20firm's%20strong%20returns%20this%20year%2C%20which%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20firm%20told%20Business%20Insider%20was%2034.1%25%20for%20its%20long-short%20fund%20and%2044.5%25%20for%20its%20long-only%20offering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Chase%20Coleman's%20Tiger%20Global%20added%20more%20than%20a%20million%20shares%20of%20Nvidia%20to%20its%20book%20after%20not%20owning%20it%2012%20months%20earlier.%20Maverick%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20increased%20its%20Nvidia%20stake%2010-fold%20since%20the%20start%20of%202022's%20third%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETudor%20Investment%20Corporation%20also%20grew%20its%20position%20from%20fewer%20than%208%2C000%20shares%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20to%20179%2C000%20shares%20worth%20about%20%2476%20million%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20ignoring%20options.%20However%2C%20it%20slashed%20its%20holdings%20to%20fewer%20than%2015%2C000%20shares%20worth%20about%20%246%20million%20by%20the%20end%20of%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20remained%20divided%20on%20Nvidia%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%20The%20Bill%20%26amp%3B%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%20Trust%20and%20Dalio's%20Bridgewater%20Associates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-dalio-gates-foundation-bridgewater-portfolio-tech-microchips-ai-2023-11%5C%22%3Eboth%20established%3C%2Fa%3E%20small%20Nvidia%20stakes.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Short%26quot%3B%20investor%20Michael%20Burry's%20Scion%20Asset%20Management%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbig-short-michael-burry-nvidia-stock-portfolio-microchips-etf-scion-2023-11%5C%22%3Epurchased%20bearish%20put%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20an%20index%20of%20microchip%20stocks%20that%20counts%20Nvidia%20as%20its%20third-largest%20holding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELone%20Pine%20and%20Viking%20Global%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-julian-robertsons-tiger-network-spans-hundreds-of-funds-2019-11%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EConnecticut-based%20Tiger%20Cubs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20bought%20into%20Nvidia%20during%20the%20year%20and%20sold%20out%20entirely.%20Lone%20Pine%20bought%20over%20600%2C000%20shares%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20but%20sold%20them%20in%20the%20second%2C%20while%20Viking%20purchased%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20shares%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20only%20to%20sell%20them%20in%20the%20third.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETesla%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20electric-vehicle%20company%20have%20surged%20by%20106%25%20this%20year.%C2%A0Musk%20has%20been%20touting%20Tesla's%20AI%20prospects%20for%20a%20while%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20company's%20autonomous-driving%20and%20humanoid-robot%20projects%2C%20which%20may%20help%20explain%20the%20stock%20surge%20this%20year.%20Moreover%2C%20Tesla%20shares%20nosedived%20by%20nearly%2070%25%20in%202022%2C%20giving%20them%20plenty%20of%20ground%20to%20make%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20and%20Soros'%20funds%20eliminated%20sizeable%20positions%20in%20Tesla%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Tepper's%20firm%2C%20ignoring%20options%2C%20bought%20150%2C000%20shares%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20but%20sold%20them%20all%20over%20the%20next%20three%20months.%20Simons'%20RenTech%20also%20went%20from%20owning%204%20million%20shares%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20to%20holding%20717%2C000%20shares%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September.%20As%20for%20Dan%20Sundheim's%20D1%20Capital%2C%20it%20sold%20its%20entire%20Tesla%20stake%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20several%20longstanding%20shareholders%20including%20Ron%20Baron's%20Baron%20Capital%2C%20Cathie%20Wood's%20Ark%20Investment%20Management%2C%20and%20Jennison%20Associates%2C%20a%20growth-equity%20manager.%20But%20it%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most-shorted%20stocks%20on%20the%20market.%20Hedge%20funds%20tracked%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%20held%20short%20positions%20worth%20almost%20%2419%20billion%20as%20of%20October%2031%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketwatch.com%2Fstory%2Ftesla-is-still-hedge-funds-favorite-short-after-stock-saw-heavy-losses-in-october-ed50e82d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarketWatch%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20a%20Goldman%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20enterprise-software%20giant's%20shares%20slumped%20by%20nearly%2030%25%20in%202022%2C%20but%20have%20jumped%20by%2055%25%20to%20near-record%20highs%20this%20year%2C%20boosting%20its%20market%20value%20to%20around%20%242.8%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buying%20frenzy%20was%20partly%20fueled%20by%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-investing-billions-into-chatgpt-creator-openai-partnership-2023-1%5C%22%3Ereported%20%2410%20billion%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20spring%20in%20Sam%20Altman's%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20the%20innovative%20chatbot%20that%20brought%20AI%20hype%20into%20the%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20was%20already%20a%20widely%20owned%20stock%20prior%20to%20this%20year%2C%20but%20several%20top-flight%20investors%20have%20boosted%20their%20exposure%20to%20it.%20Tepper's%20Appaloosa%20has%20raised%20its%20stake%20from%20235%2C000%20shares%20worth%20%2456%20million%20at%20the%20end%20of%20December%2C%20to%201.6%20million%20shares%20worth%20%24516%20million%20nine%20months%20later.%20Tudor%20Jones'%20firm%20also%20bolstered%20its%20holdings%2C%20excluding%20options%2C%20from%207%2C300%20shares%20to%20193%2C000%20shares%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen's%20Point72%20also%20quadrupled%20its%20stake%20to%20just%20over%202%20million%20shares%20in%20the%20nine%20months%20to%20September%2C%20while%20Dalio's%20Bridgewater%20grew%20its%20position%20from%20about%2017%2C000%20shares%20to%20over%20200%2C000%20in%20that%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Laffont's%20Coatue%2C%20it%20increased%20its%20Microsoft%20position%20by%20nearly%2010-fold%20in%20the%20space%20of%2012%20months.%20Light%20Street%20and%20Tiger%20Global%20also%20boosted%20their%20Microsoft%20stakes%20in%20the%20year%20to%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20Gore's%20Generation%20Investment%20Management%2C%20Loeb's%20Third%20Point%2C%20and%20Druckenmiller's%20Duquesne%20Family%20Office%20also%20boosted%20their%20Microsoft%20holdings%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20billionaire%20Lee%20Ainslie's%20fund%20slashed%20its%20Microsoft%20position%20in%20half%20in%20the%20year%20to%20September%2030.%20Lone%20Pine%20and%20Viking%20also%20pared%20their%20Microsoft%20stakes%20by%2036%25%20and%2014%25%20respectively%20over%20the%20