is%20nothing%20to%20suggest%20it%20was%20suspicious%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20our%20investigation%20is%20as%20thorough%20as%20possible%20to%20confirm%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Detective%20Chief%20Superintendent%20(DCI)%20James%20Conway%2C%20responsible%20for%20local%20policing%20in%20the%20Tower%20Hamlets%20area%20of%20Canary%20Wharf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20this%2C%20we%20are%20releasing%20a%20CCTV%20image%20of%20Gurashman%20that%20was%20taken%20before%20his%20disappearance%20and%20would%20like%20anyone%20who%20may%20have%20seen%20him%20in%20the%20Marsh%20Wall%20area%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20Thursday%2C%2014%20December%20and%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Friday%2C%2015%20December%2C%20to%20contact%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConway%20added%20that%20this%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20tragic%20outcome%E2%80%9D%20to%20their%20missing%20persons%20inquiry%20and%20not%20the%20news%20he%20was%20hoping%20to%20give%20to%20Gurashman's%20family%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20send%20them%20my%20deepest%20condolences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20noted%20that%20although%20formal%20identification%20has%20not%20yet%20taken%20place%2C%20Gurashman's%20family%20has%20been%20informed.%20Meanwhile%2C%20anyone%20with%20information%20about%20Gurashman's%20movements%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20call%20101%20quoting%20the%20reference%20CAD5787%2F15Dec.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20widespread%20social%20media%20appeals%20by%20the%20Indian%20student%20community%20in%20the%20UK%20after%20the%20Sikh%20student%20was%20reported%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20a%20tragic%2C%20heartbreaking%20loss%20of%20one%20of%20our%20beautiful%20lives.%20I%20had%20spoken%20to%20his%20father%20and%20friends%20only%20some%20days%20ago%20when%20we%20first%20found%20out%20he%20was%20missing%20and%20had%20been%20praying%20for%20his%20safe%20discovery%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sanam%20Arora%2