0players%20to%20their%20squad.%20According%20to%20the%20IPL%20rules%2C%20teams%20can%20take%20part%20in%20swap%20deals%20or%20all-cash%20deals%20for%20cricketers%20among%20themselves%20during%20the%20ongoing%20trade%20window.%20The%20window%20opened%20on%20December%2020%20-%20a%20day%20after%20the%20auction%20ended%20-%20and%20will%20now%20be%20operational%20until%20a%20month%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%202024%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20window%20was%20also%20opened%20ahead%20of%20the%20auction%20with%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20trades%20being%20the%20return%20of%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20the%20number%20of%20trades%20that%20each%20team%20can%20do%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20trade%20window%2C%20all%20the%20deals%20will%20have%20to%20approved%20by%20the%20IPL%20governing%20council.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0Mitchell%C2%A0Starc%C2%A0surpassed%20his%20Australian%20bowling%20partner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20become%20the%20most%20expensive%20buy%20in%20IPL%20history%20with%20an%20eye%20popping%20bid%20of%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20as%20pacers%20attracted%20big%20moolah%20at%20the%20auction%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20after%20Cummins%20fetched%20an%20unprecedented%20pay%20packet%20of%2020.50%20crore%20from%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%2C%C2%A0Starc%C2%A0raised%20the%20bar%20when%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20made%20a%20multi%20million%20dollar%20bid%20for%20the%20left-arm%20pacer%20who%20last%20played%20in%20the%20IPL%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20are%20the%20unpredictable%20ways%20of%20IPL%20that%20the%20one%20third%20of%20the%20formidable%20Australian%20pace%20trio%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Josh%20Hazlewood%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1040-josh-hazlewood-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJosh%20Hazlewood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20went%20unsold%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20auction%20from%20a%20base%20price%20of%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Titans%20and%20KKR%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20long%20and%20exhilarating%20bidding%20battle%20for%C2%A0Starc%C2%A0before%20the%20latter%20lapped%20him%20up%20for%20a%20record%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarc%2C%2033%2C%20has%20usually%20prioritised%20international%20duty%20over%20IPL%20but%20decided%20to%20enter%20the%20auction%20with%20one%20eye%20on%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20that%20follows%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20only%20played%20only%20two%20seasons%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20taking%2034%20wickets%20in%2027%20games%20at%20an%20average%20of%2020.38.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Cummins%20has%20been%20a%20regular%20at%20the%20IPL%20but%20skipped%20the%202023%20edition%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20Ashes%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20intense%20bidding%20war%20followed%20for%20Cummins%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20and%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20raising%20their%20paddles%20frenetically%20to%20secure%20the%20services%20of%20the%20fast%20bowling%20all-rounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20it%20was%20SRH%20who%20broke%20the%20bank%20for%20Cummins%2C%20who%20drew%20the%20highest-ever%20bid%20surpassing%20the%20Rs%2018.5%20crore%20that%20Punjab%20Kings%20had%20shelled%20out%20for%20England's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sam%20Curran%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108668-sam-curran-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESam%20Curran%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Cummins%20attracted%20h