Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20a%20key%20BJP%20ally%2C%20and%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20till%20August%20last%20year%2C%20when%20he%20walked%20out%20in%20dramatic%20fashion%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20RJD.%20That%20took%20the%20BJP%20by%20surprise%20and%20the%20saffron%20party%20has%20been%20fiercely%20critical%20of%20the%20JDU%20leader%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20controversy%20last%20month%20in%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20-%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20criticised%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F%2522How%2520Low%2520Will%2520They%2520Stoop%3F%2522%2520PM%2520Slams%2520Nitish%2520Kumar%2520For%2520Controversial%2520Comment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bindecent%20language%26quot%3B%20while%20discussing%20the%20role%20of%20women's%20education%20in%20population%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20Sushil%20Modi%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20insulted%20women...%20nobody%20will%20take%20him%20seriously%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20Delhi%20counterpart%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20set%20off%20a%20flurry%20of%20speculation%20Wednesday%20after%20naming%20Congress%20boss%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20as%20INDIA's%20PM%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20declined%2C%20calling%20for%20focus%20on%20winning%20the%20election%20before%20discussing%20PM%20candidates%2C%20but%20the%20proposal%20made%20headlines%2C%20particularly%20after%20sources%20said%20Nitish%20Kumar%20left%20the%20meeting%20in%20a%20huff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-proposes-mallikarjun-kharge-as-india-blocs-pm-face-sources-4703787%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKharge%20As%20INDIA%20PM%20Face%3F%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Surprise%20Pitch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20repor