elements%2Fdownload_file_division.jsp%3Fnum_id%3DMTA3Nzg%3D%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cshould%20be%20not%20used%20in%20children%20below%20four%20years%20of%20age%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ordered%20that%20manufacturers%20apply%20a%20warning%20label%20to%20this%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%20asked%20state%20drug%20controllers%20on%20Monday%20(December%2018)%20to%20direct%20manufacturers%20in%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions%20to%20apply%20the%20label%20to%20the%20drug%20mixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rajeev%20Singh%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20drug%20controller%20general%20and%20head%20of%20the%20CDSCO%2C%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20an%20expert%20committee%20that%20met%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mixture%20in%20question%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98fixed-dose%20combination%E2%80%99%20(FDC)%20of%20chlorpheniramine%20maleate%20and%20phenylephrine%20hydrochloride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhealthcare-pharmaceuticals%2Findia-bans-anti-cold-drug-combination-kids-aged-under-four-2023-12-20%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20FDC%20is%20used%20in%20syrups%20and%20tablets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20treat%20common%20cold%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECough%20syrups%20manufactured%20in%20India%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20children%20both%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%20were%20linked%20to%20their%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20said%20that%20cough%20syrups%20made%20in%20India%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fhealth-coughsyrup-india%2F%5C%22%3Elinked%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20141%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Gambia%2C%20Uzbekistan%20and%20Cameroon%20over%202022%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20agency%20also%20reported%20that