.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20earthen%20pots%20contain%20soil%20from%20villages%20and%20farmlands%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Back%20in%20March%202021%2C%20when%20I%20travelled%20with%20farmer%20outfits%20and%20covered%20a%20journey%20of%20more%20than%20650%20kms%20from%20southern%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Banswara%20to%20the%20Shahjahanpur%20border%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20collective%20camaraderie%20among%20farmers%2C%20who%20spoke%20about%20the%20threat%20they%20felt%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fexplained-what-are-the-three-farm-laws-and-what-made-them-controversial-7738991.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20farm%20laws%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20called%20the%20exercise%20of%20collecting%20soil%20in%20these%20pots%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emitti%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Esatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20satyagraha%20of%20the%20soil%2C%20a%20movement%20based%20on%20Gandhian%20principles%20of%20non-violent%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20I%20heard%20Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%E2%80%99s%20angry%20diatribe%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20wherein%20he%20asserted%20his%20identity%20as%20a%20farmer%20and%20Jat%20while%20condemning%20a%20video%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fshameful-ridiculous-unacceptable-jagdeep-dhankar-slams-trinamool-mp-kalyan-banerjee-for-mimicry-act-hits-out-at-rahul-gandhi-for-making-video%2Farticleshow%2F106127501.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20mimicking%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20think%20of%20my%20fellow%20farmers%20in%20the%20Shahjahanpur%20protests%2C%20who%20despite%20being%20ridiculed%20and%20vilified%20so%20frequently%20by%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20got%20little%20by%20way%20of%20support%20from%20figures%20such%20as%20Dhankhar%2C%20who%20at%20that%20point%20was%20the%20Governor%20of%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20far%20from%20playing%20the%20victim%20card%2C%20they%20tenaciously%20continued%20their%20satyagraha%20against%20the%20three%20laws%20till%20they%20were%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20angry%20outburst%2C%20Dhankhar%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1988365%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehis%20background%20as%20a%20Jat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20being%20from%20the%20farming%20class%20was%20being%20%E2%80%98insulted.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20individual%2C%20take%20on%20me%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20on%20my%20background%20as%20a%20farmer%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20on%20my%20background%20as%20a%20community%20member.%20Institution%20of%20Chairman%20has%20been%20ravaged%20and%20that%20too%20by%20a%20political%20party%20that%20has%20gone%20so%20far%20that%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20a%20senior%20one%2C%20videographs%20the%20other%20member%E2%80%A6%20On%20Instagram%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20your%20party%20put%20a%20video%20which%20was%20withdrawn%20later.%20That%20was%20a%20shame%20to%20me.%20You%20used%20the%20official%20Twitter%20handle%20of%20the%20spokesperson%20to%20demean%20me%2C%20insult%20me%2C%20insult%20my%20background%20as%20a%20farmer%2C%20my%20position%20as%20a%20Jat%2C%20insult%20my%20position%20as%20Chairman.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20worth%20mentioning%20that%20the%20protests%20outside%20the%20parliament%20by%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20being%20held%20at%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20instance%20of%20the%20suspension%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F141-opposition-mps-suspended-so-far-are-they-allowed-to-enter-parliament-check-list-of-restrictions-11703057026922.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E143%20MPs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20which%20Dhankhar%20too%20played%20his%20part%20by%20suspending%20opposition%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20who%20were%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20over%20the%20recent%20intrusion%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Dhankhar%20suspended%20the%20house%20as%20well%20as%20its%20members%2C%20he%20clearly%20does%20not%20want%20to%20face%20any%20criticism%2C%20citing%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20holds%20a%20constitutional%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20issue%20snowballed%20into%20a%20controversy%2C%20Dhankhar%20has%20found%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-dials-vp-dhankhar-as-mimicry-row-heats-up-expresses-pain-over-abject-theatrics-101703046457739.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esupport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20PM%20Modi%2C%20and%20even%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%20While%20many%20would%20argue%20that%20mimicking%20is%20an%20acceptable%20form%20of%20criticism%20and%20that%20even%20if%20he%20is%20on%20a%20constitutional%20post%2C%20he%20is%20not%20beyond%20criticism%2C%20by%20invoking%20his%20caste%20and%20farming%20background%2C%20Dhankhar%20has%20created%20an%20impression%20that%20criticising%20him%20is%20the%20criticism%20of%20the%20farming%20class.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20here%2C%20that%20I%20would%20like%20to%20disagree%20with%20the%20honourable%20vice-president.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20fellow%20Jat%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20whose%20primary%20occupation%20has%20been%20farming%20for%20several%20generations%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20notice%20the%20clear%20double%20standards%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20seeing%20one%20section%20of%20Jat%20farmers%20under%20the%20anti-national%20lens%20while%20crying%20foul%20and%20asserting%20one%E2%80%99s%20Jat%20identity%20when%20convenient.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20V-P%20Dhankhar%20has%20forgotten%20that%20when%20medalled%20wrestlers%20who%20are%20also%20daughters%20of%20Jat%20farmers%2C%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fwrestlers-protest-against-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-hanging-on-in-troubled-hunt-for-justice%2Farticle67004574.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprotesting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20a%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20there%20were%20concerted%20efforts%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20sportspersons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Jat%20outfits%20across%20the%20country%20stood%20firmly%20behind%20the%20sportspersons%20at%20the%20time%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20a%20similar%20emotive%20speech%20from%20Dhankhar%20on%20the%20targeted%20harassment%20of%20Jat%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20Congress%20MP%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20without%20naming%20Gandhi%2C%20Dhankhar%20slammed%20him%20for%20recording%20the%20video%20of%20the%20TMC%20MP%20mimicking%20him%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20vocal%20in%20the%20support%20of%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%2C%20much%20like%20his%20public%20support%20for%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20during%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20by%20identifying%20himself%20as%20a%20Jat%20while%20sitting%20on%20a%20constitutional%20position%2C%20he%20has%20rightly%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20representation%20of%20different%20communities%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20other%20spheres%20of%20the%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20vice-president%E2%80%99s%20native%20village%20is%20in%20Jhunjhunu%2C%20a%20district%20which%20sends%20thousands%20of%20youngsters%20to%20the%20Army%20%E2%80%93%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20whom%20are%20Jats%20%E2%80%93%20every%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Shekhawati%20region%20comprising%20districts%20such%20as%20Jhunjhunu%20and%20Sikar%20have%20been%20witnessing%20constant%20protests%20over%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fagnipath-protests-agniveer-scheme-violence-narendra-modi-bjp-unemployed-youth%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAgniveer%20scheme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20V-P%20is%20yet%20to%20break%20his%20silence%20on%20an%20issue%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20future%20of%20thousands%20of%20Jat%20youngsters%20from%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20the%20Jat%20trope%20and%20raising%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20issues%20is%20alright%20till%20the%20time%20it%20is%20not%20only%20restricted%20to%20those%20issues%20that%20conveniently%20suit%20the%20ruling%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhil%20Chaudhary%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20based%20in%20Rajasthan.%20He%20posts%20on%20X%20%40akhilchaudhary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703148006000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21140803%2FUntitled-design-7.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-jat-farmer-vice-president-kalyan-banerjee%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22...and%20yet%20he%20had%20remained%20silent%20then.%20His%20invocation%20of%20the%20community%20is%20restricted%20to%20only%20instances%20that%20conveniently%20suit%20the%20ruling%20party.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-jat-farmer-vice-president-kalyan-banerjee%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C