ced%20him%20to%20strip.%20He%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20kept%20pleading%20with%20them%20to%20let%20him%20go%2C%20but%20they%20continued%20to%20thrash%20him%20and%20film%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspects%20also%20threatened%20him%20that%20they%20would%20get%20him%20murdered%20if%20he%20went%20to%20police.%20The%20boy%20someone%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20spot%20and%20fled%20to%20his%20home.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20the%20suspects%20shared%20the%20video%20online.%20The%20boy%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20is%20embarrassed%20to%20even%20step%20out%20in%20this%20neighbourhood%20after%20the%20video%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703146140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ftk7sm67_jhansi-boy_625x300_21_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-class-10-boy-stripped-thrashed-on-video-by-classmates-over-rs-200-4715068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2016-year-old%20boy%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jhansi%20was%20forced%20to%20drink%20alcohol%2C%20stripped%20and%20thrashed%20by%20his%20classmates%20after%20the%20Class%2010%20student%20asked%20one%20of%20them%20to%20return%20Rs%20200%20he%20had%20borrowed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-class-10-boy-stripped-thrashed-on-video-by-classmates-over-rs-200-4715068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-class-10-boy-stripped-thrashed-on-video-by-classmates-over-rs-200-4715068%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-class-10-boy-stripped-thrashed-on-video-by-classmates-over-rs-200-4715068%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Fire%20At%20Iconic%20Gopaldas%20Building%20At%20Delhi's%20Connaught%20Place%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20fire%20broke%20out%20this%20afternoon%20at%20the%20iconic%20Gopaldas%20