m%2Fdelhi-news%2Fvideo-fire-at-iconic-gopaldas-building-at-delhis-connaught-place-4715069%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20brings%20this%20Apple%20Watch%20feature%20to%20its%20smartwatches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703146050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106177642%2Cimgsize-43600.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fsamsung-brings-this-apple-watch-feature-to-its-own-smartwatches%2Farticleshow%2F106177642.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samsung%20has%20added%20a%20medication%20tracking%20feature%20to%20the%20Samsung%20Health%20app.%20The%20feature%20allows%20users%20to%20easily%20log%20and%20manage%20both%20prescription%20and%20over-the-counter%20medications.%20Users%20can%20enter%20the%20name%20of%20a%20medication%20to%20get%20detailed%20information%20about%20it%2C%20including%20descriptions%20and%20possible%20side%20effects.%20They%20can%20also%20log%20the%20shape%20and%20color%20of%20their%20medications%20for%20easy%20identification.%20The%20feature%20includes%20alerts%20to%20remind%20users%20when%20to%20take%20their%20medications%20and%20when%20to%20refill%20them.%20Galaxy%20Watch%20users%20will%20also%20receive%20reminders%20on%20their%20wrist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fsamsung-brings-this-apple-watch-feature-to-its-own-smartwatches%2Farticleshow%2F106177642.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22H-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Dates%2C%20Eligibility%20Criteria%2C%20Application%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20is%20introducing%20a%20pilot%20programme%20to%20restart%20the%20renewal%20process%20for%20qualified%20H-1B%20non-immigrant%20visa%20applicants%20within%20the%20country.%20This%20initiative%20aims%20to%20assess%20the%20Department's%20technical%20and%20operational%20capabilities%20in%20reinstating%20domestic%20visa%20renewals.%20The%20first%20phase%20is%20for%2020%2C000%20people%20and%20is%20open%20only%20to%20Indians%20and%20Canadians.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EH-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Dates%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20State%20Department%20will%20receive%20applications%20for%20the%20H-1B%20pilot%20programme%20from%20January%2029%20to%20April%201%2C%202024.%20Eligible%20applicants%20are%20encouraged%20to%20apply%20online%20within%20the%20three-month%20application%20window.%20The%20department%20has%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20midnight%20on%20April%2015%2C%202024%2C%20to%20submit%20written%20comments%20and%20related%20materials.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20plans%20to%20open%20approximately%204%2C000%20application%20slots%20for%20H-1B%20visa%20renewals%20every%20week.%20These%20slots%20will%20be%20available%20on%20the%20following%20dates%3A%20January%2029%2C%20February%205%2C%20February%2012%2C%20February%2019%2C%20and%20February%2026.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EH-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Eligibility%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnApplicants%20must%20meet%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnly%20H-1B%20visa%20renewals%20are%20processed%20during%20the%20pilot%20phase%3B%20other%20visa%20types%20are%20not%20included.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20to%20be%20renewed%20must%20have%20been%20issued%20by%20Mission%20Canada%20between%20January%201%2C%202020%2C%20and%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20or%20by%20Mission%20India%20from%20February%201%2C%202021%2C%20to%20September%2030%2C%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEligibility%20for%20a%20waiver%20of%20the%20in-person%20interview%20is%20required.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20have%20previously%20submitted%20ten%20fingerprints%20to%20the%20Department%20for%20a%20past%20visa%20application.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20should%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20a%20nonimmigrant%20visa%20issuance%20fee%2C%20also%20known%20as%20a%20reciprocity%20fee.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20prior%20visa%20must%20not%20have%20a%20'clearance%20received'%20annotation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20cannot%20have%20a%20visa%20ineligibility%20that%20requires%20a%20waiver%20for%20issuance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20have%20an%20approved%20and%20unexpired%20H-1B%20petition.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20applicant's%20most%20recent%20admission%20to%20the%20U.S.%20must%20have%20been%20in%20H-1B%20status.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20be%20currently%20maintaining%20H-1B%20status%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20period%20of%20authorized%20admission%20in%20H-1B%20status%20should%20not%20have%20expired.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApplicants%20must%20intend%20to%20reenter%20the%20U.S.%20in%20H-1B%20status%20after%20a%20temporary%20period%20abroad.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EH-1B%20Visa%20Pilot%20Programme%3A%20Application%20Details%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20submit%20applications%2C%20visit%20here%20(%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Fus-visas%2Femployment%2Fdomestic-renewal.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703231553446000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3RLftzqZ8ucMPYutTV9wZq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Fus-visas%2Femployment%2Fdomestic-renewal.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2F%3Cwbr%3Econtent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Fus-visas%2F%3Cwbr%3Eemployment%2Fdomestic-renewal.%3Cwbr%3Ehtml%3C%2Fa%3E).%20An%20overview%20of%20this%20regulation%20is%20accessible%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.regulations.gov%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1703231553446000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0T8Tvqgnft997S_Zj8yO5e%5C%22%20href%3D%