r%20people%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20and%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Canadian%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fcanada-accuses-indian-government-of-assassinating-sikh-citizen-in-vancouver-expels-senior-diplomat%5C%22%3ETrudeau%20had%20stood%20in%20the%20lower%20chamber%20of%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20an%20explosive%20allegation%20that%20there%20was%20credible%20information%20that%20potentially%20links%20agents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20whom%20India%20had%20described%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20countries%20expelled%20one%20diplomat%20each%2C%20but%20India%20went%20further%20and%20stopped%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20which%20was%20eventually%20resumed%20after%20a%20month.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20also%20demanded%20parity%20in%20diplomatic%20representation%2C%20which%20led%20Canada%20to%20recall%2047%20diplomats%20posted%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2029%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20US%20prosecutors%20filed%20a%20new%20and%20detailed%20indictment%20that%20charged%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20for%20a%20thwarted%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20The%20indictment%20had%20also%20accused%20an%20unnamed%2C%20but%20identified%2C%20Indian%20government%20official%20for%20being%20the%20main%20mastermind.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20its%20response%20to%20Canada%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20announced%20that%20a%20high-level%20committee%20of%20inquiry%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20look%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinputs%E2%80%9D%20provided%20by%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20questions%20in%20parliament%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fone-has-provided-inputs-another-hasnt-jaishankar-on-indias-differing-responses-to-us-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexternal%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20said%20that%20the%20disparity%20in%20response%20was%20due%20to%20Canada%20not%20sharing%20any%20evidence%20with%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fpolitics%2Frevealing-allegations-on-nijjar-death-meant-to-put-a-chill-on-india-trudeau-says-1.6683983%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Trudeau%20had%20committed%20to%20disclose%20evidence%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20the%20US%20did%20once%20the%20investigation%20reached%20that%20stage.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20that%20US%20authorities%20had%20started%20their%20investigation%20into%20the%20attempted%20murder%20much%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCanada%20is%20investigating%20a%20murder%20and%20there%20are%20different%20stakes%20involved%20in%20that%20and%20our%20justice%20system%20has%20different%20processes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20the%20first%20time%20commented%20on%20the%20allegations%20made%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20to%20kill%20the%20Sikh%20separatist%20in%20New%20York%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnarendra-modi-pannun-plot-us-ties%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan