C%20has%20not%20answered%20the%20fundamental%20question%20%E2%80%93%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20have%20moved%20beyond%20security%20and%20focussed%20on%20the%20grievances%20expressed%20by%20the%20young%20people%20behind%20the%20incident.%20As%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-sees-security-breach-as-two-persons-jump-into-lok-sabha-from-public-gallery%2Farticle67633757.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Delhi%20police%20have%20not%20yet%20found%20any%20links%20between%20the%20accused%20and%20any%20terror%20group%20or%20political%20party%20(though%20the%20accused%20have%20all%20been%20arrested%20under%20the%20stringent%20Indian%20anti%20terror%20law%2C%20the%20UAPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-sees-security-breach-as-two-persons-jump-into-lok-sabha-from-public-gallery%2Farticle67633757.ece%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0told%20the%20police%20that%20they%20were%20upset%20with%20unemployment%20and%20rising%20prices.%20This%20is%20certainly%20plausible.%20Youth%20unemployment%20in%20India%20hovers%20around%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fpolarisation-damaging-foundations-of-indias-growth-kaushik-basu%2F968914%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20staggering%2024%25%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20is%20among%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20world.%20And%20for%20graduates%20under%2025%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20estimates%20that%20this%20number%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F374264645_State_of_Working_India_2023_Social_Identities_and_Labour_Market_Outcomes%5C%22%3Erises%20to%2042%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20explain%20why%2C%20in%20a%20country%20a%20few%20months%20away%20from%20a%20general%20election%2C%20a%20group%20felt%20so%20disenfranchised%20that%20risking%20their%20freedom%20to%20protest%20inside%20parliament%20felt%20like%20the%20only%20option.%20Their%20very%20choice%20of%20inspiration%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20a%2020th-century%20revolutionary%20fighting%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20colonial%20government%20in%20India%2C%20speaks%20to%20a%20high%20level%20of%20alienation%20from%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20belief%20in%2C%20the%20current%20electoral%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20we%20must%20then%20ask%20is%20why%20has%20the%20political%20discourse%20in%20India%20failed%20to%20capture%20and%20channel%20this%20anger%20with%20policy%20into%20electoral%20politics%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20respect%2C%20the%20last%20decade%20is%20interesting.%20Going%20by%20electoral%20results%20alone%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20make%20the%20argument%20that%20despite%20a%20few%20losses%20here%20and%20there%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20juggernaut%20remains%20largely%20intact.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20a%20time%20where%20the%20same%20BJP-led%20government%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20walk%20back%20on%20fairly%20significant%20policy%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%20apparent%20contradiction%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20begin%20with%20examining%20the%20deliberate%20weakening%20of%20the%20legislature%20itself%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarunabh%20Khaitan%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.degruyter.com%2Fdocument%2Fdoi%2F10.1515%2Flehr-2020-2009%2Fhtml%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Eanalysing%20institutional%20erosion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20BJP%20term%2C%20offers%20several%20examples%2C%20including%20the%20rush%20to%20tenuously%20classify%20Bills%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmoney%20Bills%E2%80%9D%20and%20thereby%20bypass%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20altogether%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20processes%20like%20the%20guillotine%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20speaker%20to%20put%20Bills%20to%20the%20vote%20without%20allowing%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsLRO4qs6Q-Q%3Fsi%3DvM2kBZN9am67DM_3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20from%20the%20outset%20also%20disregarded%20lawmaking%20conventions%20(like%20select%20committees)%20designed%20to%20bring%20in%20closer%20legislative%20scrutiny%20of%20Bills%20prior%20to%20passing%20them%20into%20laws.%20As%20per%20PRS%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20bills%20sent%20to%20select%20committees%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnda-narendra-modi-parliament-functioning%5C%22%3Esignificantly%20lower%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20first%20term%20than%20in%20the%20preceding%20decade%2C%20and%20has%20almost%20become%20non%20existent%20in%20this%20ongoing%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20possible%2C%20this%20government%20has%20sought%20to%20bypass%20legislature%20altogether%20and%20has%20preferred%20to%20operate%20through%20ordinances%2C%20and%20opposition%20strategies%20like%20walk%20outs%20and%20boycotts%20of%20parliament%20have%20only%20reinforced%20the%20overall%20impression%20of%20helplessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20India%2C%20but%20usually%2C%20when%20one%20democratic%20institution%20is%20weakened%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20other%20institutions%20have%20held%20firm.%20The%20judiciary%20for%20example%20triggered%20the%20Emergency%20itself%20by%20holding%20firm%20on%20its%20disqualification%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20for%20electoral%20malpractice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20last%20decade%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20gradual%20decline%20in%20the%20public%20expectation%20that%20the%20courts%20will%20step%20in%20to%20check%20the%20executive.%20And%20from%20upholding%20the%20classification%20of%20Aadhar%20as%20a%20money%20Bill%2C%20to%20the%20delays%20in%20hearing%20campaign%20finance%20challenges%2C%20to%20the%20verdict%20on%20Babri%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20argue%20that%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20has%20offered%20any%20meaningful%20check%20to%20the%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20simultaneous%20weakening%20of%20two%20major%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20legislature%20and%20the%20judiciary%20%E2%80%93%20resistance%20to%20policy%2C%20both%20small%20and%20large%2C%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20this%20has%20been%20more%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%202016%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20issued%20a%20notification%20that%20would%20restrict%20workers%20from%20making%20withdrawals%20of%20their%20own%20savings%20from%20provident%20funds%20until%20retirement%20age.%20Almost%20immediately%2C%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20mostly%20female%20garment%20factory%20workers%20collected%20in%20Bangalore%20to%20protest.%20The%20labour%20unions%20took%20the%20matter%20up%20and%20ultimately%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fwealth%2Fpersonal-finance-news%2Fgovernment-rolls-back-restrictions-on-withdrawal-of-provident-fund%2Farticleshow%2F51896900.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Erestrictions%20were%20rolled%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20collective%20action%20in%202017%2C%20by%20a%20very%20different%20socio-economic%20class%20of%20citizens%2C%20ensured%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftattva.substack.com%2Fp%2Fwhat-we-can-learn-from-the-withdrawal%5C%22%3Ewithdrawal%20of%20the%20FDRI%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20second%20term%2C%20this%20method%20of%20protestors%20bypassing%20political%20opposition%20and%20engaging%20directly%20with%20the%20government%20through%20on-ground%20protest%20has%20taken%20centre%20stage%20and%20successfully%20challenged%20legislation%20at%20the%20very%20heart%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%20and%202020%2C%20widespread%20protests%20ensured%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20and%20the%20proposed%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens.%20Beginning%20in%20the%20end%20of%202020%20and%20continuing%20into%202021%2C%20the%20country%20saw%20the%20largest%20and%20longest%20farmer%20agitation%20the%20world%2C%20which%20ended%20only%20with%20the%20repeal%20of%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20that%20were%20set%20to%20significantly%20privatise%20Indian%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fmass-protest-decade-vincent-bevins-book-review%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Mass%20Protest%20Decade%20of%202010-2020%20Left%20Us%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98Missing%20Revolution%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20protests%20were%20diverse%2C%20but%20they%20shared%20certain%20commonalities%20%E2%80%93%20first%2C%20they%20were%20highly%20specific%20in%20nature%20with%20very%20specific%20demands%2C%20usually%20the%20repeal%20of%20a%20law%20or%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20they%20largely%20shunned%20formal%20association%20with%20political%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20though%20many%20opposition%20leaders%20offered%20their%20support%20%E2%80%93%20relying%20instead%20on%20alternative%20forms%20of%20organisation%20including%20labour%20and%20farmer%20unions%2C%20student%20unions%2C%20religious%20and%20community%20leaders%20and%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20spillover%20effect%20of%20these%20massive%20on-ground%20protests%20into%20the%20electoral%20sphere%20has%20been%20minimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20means%20is%20that%20protests%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20years%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20years%2C%20do%20not%20develop%20momentum%20and%20evolve%20into%20larger%20electoral%20movements%20seeking%20to%20unseat%20the%20government.%20Instead%20they%20play%20the%20role%20an%20opposition%20otherwise%20would%20%E2%80%93%20offering%20policy-specific%20challenges%20to%20a%20government%2C%20and%20disbanding%20when%20those%20demands%20are%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20the%20ruling%20government%20also%20sees%20them%20as%20such.%20There%20were%20far%20more%20negotiations%20with%20the%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20on%20the%20farm%20laws%20than%20there%20was%20discussion%20in%20parliament%20where%20the%20legislation%20was%20rushed%20through%20both%20houses.%20And%20unlike%20during%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Emergency%20where%20all%20of%20the%20opposition%20was%20jailed%20first%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20focussed%20its%20political%20arrests%20on%20civil%20society%2C%20journalists%20and%20Muslim%20student%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20December%2013%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67724698%5C%22%3E141%20opposition%20members%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20have%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20winter%20session%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cunruly%20behaviour%E2%80%9D%20in%20demanding%20the%20home%20minister%20address%20parliament.%20And%20apart%20from%20a%20few%20analysts%2C%20this%20mass%20suspension%20of%20the%20opposition%20from%20a%20parliamentary%20session%20where%20key%20legislation%20on%20criminal%20law%20and%20telecommunications%20censorship%20are%20to%20be%20tabled%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20triggered%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20does%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20the%20government%20has%20mass%20support%20for%20its%20actions.%20It%20merely%20speaks%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20legislature%20isn%E2%80%99t%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20the%20key%20site%20of%20resistance%20to%20government%20policy%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-last-pillar-of-indian-democracy-has-fallen%5C%22%3EThe%20Last%20Pillar%20of%20Indian%20Democracy%20Has%20Fallen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20worrying.%20While%20politics%20certainly%20is%20more%20than%20electoral%20politics%20and%20should%20include%20every%20means%20by%20which%20the%20residents%20of%20a%20country%20engage%20with%20their%20government%2C%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20on-ground%20protest%20and%20the%20sidelining%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20speaks%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20institutional%20credibility%20that%20goes%20beyond%20a%20single%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20people%20willing%20to%20make%20parliament%20the%20site%20of%20their%20protest%20are%20not%20just%20angry%20with%20the%20government%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20parliament%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20with%20access%20to%20alternative%20institutions%20like%20labour%20unions%2C%20or%20religious%20community%20leaders%20or%20caste-justice%20based%20organisations%2C%20this%20loss%20of%20faith%20has%20not%20been%20catastrophic%2C%20as%20these%20institutions%20have%20stepped%20into%20the%20void.%20They%20have%20channelled%20this%20anger%20into%20policy-specific%2C%20on-ground%20demonstrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20young%20people%20like%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20December%2013%20incident%2C%20without%20access%20to%20organised%20movements%20like%20the%20labour%20union%20movement%20or%20caste-based%20justice%20movements%2C%20their%20protests%20have%20been%20tragic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20weeks%20of%20this%20year%20should%20leave%20us%20with%20significant%20questions%20in%20our%20mind%20that%20will%20have%20ramifications%20beyond%202024.%20In%20a%20vibrant%20democracy%2C%20on-ground%20protests%20feed%20into%20and%20form%20the%20basis%20for%20electoral%20action.%20Civil%20society%2C%20the%20judiciary%2C%20parliament%20and%20the%20electoral%20process%20work%20together%20to%20hold%20governments%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20authoritarian%20regimes%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20on-ground%20protests%20erupt%20sporadically%2C%20are%20suppressed%20brutally%20and%20on%20occasion%20win%20concessions%20when%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20protest%20means%20it%20cannot%20be%20suppressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20far%20more%20comfortable%20dealing%20with%20the%20latter.%20But%20the%20preservation%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20requires%20us%20to%20slowly%20find%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20on-ground%20anger%20with%20the%20electoral%20process%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20opposition%2C%20it%20means%20making%20people%20who%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20our%20democratic%20institutions%20believe%20that%20they%20can%20and%20must%20be%20repaired%2C%20not%20cast%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsarayu-pani%5C%22%3ESarayu%20Pani%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20lawyer%20and%20tweets%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsarayupani%5C%22%3E%40sarayupani%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftattva.substack.com%2Fp%2Fa-bruised-legislature-in-a-new-building%5C%22%3Erepublished%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20Substack%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftattva.substack.com%2F%5C%22%3ETattva%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0with%20permission.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703096350000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14095043%2FGBN2cf7bMAANLsZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanger-with-state-policy-must-be-tied-to-the-electoral-process%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20politics%20is%20more%20than%20electoral%20politics%20and%20must%20include%20every%20means%20by%20which%20the%20residents%20of%20a%20country%20engage%20with%20their%20government%2C%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20on-ground%20protest%20and%20the%20sidelin