3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20he%20decide%20not%20to%20pursue%20medicine%20from%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20medical%20colleges%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20leave%20Kohima.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20he%20argues%20that%20pursuing%20his%20graduation%20at%20the%20Kohima%20Science%20College%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cplus%20point%E2%80%9D%20in%20helping%20him%20mould%20his%20craft%20as%20a%20rapper%20and%20performer.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20demands%20of%20medical%20school%2C%20maybe%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20study%20there%2C%20I%20would%20be%20a%20doctor%20now%20instead%20of%20a%20rapper%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20college%20functions%2C%20I%20would%20always%20take%20the%20opportunity%20to%20get%20on%20stage%20and%20perform%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20away%20with%20stage%20fright.%20In%20the%20years%20I%20spent%20in%20college%2C%20I%20would%20always%20request%20my%20seniors%20to%20let%20me%20perform%20on%20stage%20and%20they%20would%20give%20me%20a%20chance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20as%20he%20was%20coming%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20Anthropology%2C%20he%20began%20performing%20in%20front%20of%20live%20audiences%20and%20earning%20some%20money%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20has%20always%20been%20supportive%20of%20my%20music.%20During%20my%20college%20days%2C%20I%20never%20flunked%20out%2C%20brought%20bad%20grades%20or%20got%20held%20up%20by%20%E2%80%98back%20papers%E2%80%99.%20That%20allowed%20my%20family%20to%20trust%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20with%20my%20life.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20making%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20college%2C%20making%20music%20started%20as%20a%20hobby%20but%20soon%20turned%20into%20a%20passion.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20performed%20in%20front%20of%20a%20l